metadata.description:
THERE IS A HIDDEN IMAGE WITHIN THIS ART PIECE!
Can you see it?

Remember the 'Magic Eye' book craze of the 90s? This is the same science!

Instructions: center the image right up to your nose. It should be blurry. Focus as though you are looking through the image into the distance. Very slowly move the image away from your face until your eyes adjust and the hidden image suddenly becomes visible! (Failing that lookup how to see Autostereograms on google!)

View the image on Twitter: 
https://twitter.com/cryptoparadoxx/status/1246768992582238208
metadata.name: Invisible Currency - Autostereogram - FIND THE HIDDEN IMAGE!
